<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Borrado del Actor</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <figure>
        <img src="/img/logo-DH.png" alt="Logo Digital House">
      </figure>
    <h1>Estas seguro de querer borrar este/a actor/actriz: <%= actor.first_name %> <%= actor.last_name %>???</h1>
